channel.title: SRL Bank Withdraw
channel.description:
Hey everyone,
I'm currently making an alkharid smelter using SRL.
I just started this morning but I'm having a problem with the Withdraw function (withdraw and withdraw2) They both seem to not right click on the actual ore =/, anyone else had thise problem and/or now how to fix it?
I'm thinking of just using a find object function instead now, but if anyone nows a way I could fix the withdraw ones that'd be really helpfull-
Thanks in advance
-1337.
